﻿@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #FAEBD7;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #FAEBD7;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

        <p>
            Bargain Balloons is dedicated to protecting your personal information. This policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your data when you use our website [www.yourcompanywebsite.com].

            What Information We Collect
            Personal Information: When you register, make a purchase, or contact us, we collect your name, email, address, and payment details.
            Usage Data: We gather information about how you use our site, such as your IP address and the pages you visit.

            Cookies: Small files that help us remember your preferences and improve your experience.

            How We Use Your Information
            To Provide Services: Processing orders and responding to your inquiries.

            To Communicate: Sending updates and promotional offers.

            To Improve: Enhancing our website and services based on your usage.
            Sharing Your Information
            With Partners: We share information with companies that help us operate our site and process payments.
            Legal Reasons: We may share information if required by law.
            Your Choices
            Access and Update: You can update your information by logging into your account.
            Opt-Out: You can unsubscribe from promotional emails at any time.
            Cookies: Manage cookies through your browser settings.
            Security
            We use security measures to keep your information safe.

            Changes
            We may update this policy. Check this page for any changes.

            Contact Us
            If you have questions, contact us at:

            Bargain Balloons
            Email: bargainballoonsupport@gmail.com
        </p>

    </div>
</body>
</html>
